column2: SELECT p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, (p.u-p.r) as #, (p.r-p.i) as #, (p.r-p.z) as #, (p.g-p.r) as #, p.type as obj_ph_type, p.petroRad_u, p.petroRad_g, p.petroRad_r, p.petroRad_i, p.petroRad_z, p.petroRadErr_u, p.petroRadErr_g, p.petroRadErr_r, p.petroRadErr_i, p.petroRadErr_z, s.specobjid, s.class as obj_sp_type, s.subclass as obj_sp_subtype, s.z as redshift into mydb.dr1#_spec_sample from PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE s.z BETWEEN # AND # AND (p.u-p.r < = #) AND (p.r-p.i < = #) AND (p.r-p.z < = #) AND (p.g-p.r > = (p.r-p.i) + #) AND (p.u-p.r > = #* (p.r-p.z) )
